<item>
            <title>[QPID-2444] JMS client does not verify that the hostname connected to matches that specified in the servers certificate</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPID-2444</link>
                <project id="12310520" key="QPID">Qpid</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The JMS client will succeed in connecting to a broker whose certificate has a&lt;br/&gt;
random string as the common name. It should (at least as an option) verify that&lt;br/&gt;
the CN matches the hostname it believes it has connected to.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12459002">QPID-2444</key>
