                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12849220" author="rajith" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2010 15:27:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In order to enable hostname verification, you need to use ssl_verify_hostname=&apos;true&apos; in the broker URL.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ex &quot;amqp://guest:guest@test/?brokerlist=&apos;tcp://&amp;lt;hostname&amp;gt;:5671?ssl=&apos;true&apos;&amp;amp;ssl_verify_hostname=&apos;true&apos;&apos;&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12849221" author="rajith" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2010 15:29:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The SSLTest has &quot;testVerifyHostName&quot; ,  &quot;testVerifyLocalHost&apos; and &quot;testVerifyLocalHostLocalDomain&quot; as test cases for this feature.&lt;br/&gt;
This feature has been verified manually as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
